
Layout Classes:
container: Centers and provides padding by default.
grid, grid-cols-{value}: Defines grid layout and column count.
flex: Applies flexbox layout.
flex-row, flex-col: Defines flexbox direction.
justify-{value}: Justifies content within a flex container (e.g., justify-center, justify-between).
items-{value}: Aligns items in a flexbox (e.g., items-center, items-start).

Typography Classes:
text-{size}: Set font size (e.g., text-lg, text-xl, etc.).
text-{color}: Set text color (e.g., text-blue-500, text-gray-700).
font-{weight}: Set font weight (e.g., font-bold, font-light).
leading-{value}: Sets line-height (e.g., leading-snug, leading-relaxed).

Spacing Classes:
m-{value}: Margin (e.g., m-4, mt-2, ml-6).
p-{value}: Padding (e.g., p-3, pl-5, pr-2).

Button Classes (Customizable):
bg-{color}: Background color (e.g., bg-blue-500, bg-red-600).
hover:bg-{color}: Change background color on hover (e.g., hover:bg-green-700).
py-{value}: Vertical padding (e.g., py-2).
px-{value}: Horizontal padding (e.g., px-4).
rounded-{value}: Border radius (e.g., rounded-md, rounded-lg).

Utility Classes:
bg-{color}: Set background color (e.g., bg-gray-100, bg-red-500).
border, border-{color}: Add border (e.g., border-gray-400).
shadow-{size}: Add box shadow (e.g., shadow-sm, shadow-lg).
rounded-{size}: Set border radius (e.g., rounded-full, rounded-md).